            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>1. 外資累計賣超 3 日的股票<br/>台新金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)、元大台灣50反1 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00632R:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00632R\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00632R-TW</a>)、力積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6770:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6770\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6770-TW</a>)、永豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2890:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2890\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2890-TW</a>)、大聯大 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3702:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3702\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3702-TW</a>)</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>2. 外資累計賣超 2 日的股票<br/>台新金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2887:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2887\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2887-TW</a>)、元大台灣50反1 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:00632R:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/00632R\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\